<title>USA: IPO PRICING--Peregrine prices below range.</title>
<headline>IPO PRICING--Peregrine prices below range.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-04-09</dateline>
<text>
<p>Company Name	    Peregrine Systems Inc</p>
<p>   Priced At					  $9</p>
<p>   Estimated Pricing Range	     $10 - $11</p>
<p>   Number of Shares			2,300,000</p>
<p>   Lead Underwriter	   UBS Securities Inc</p>
<p>NOTE: The estimated price range for the initial public offering in Peregrine Systems Inc was reduced to $10 to $11 per share of common stock from $10 to $12.</p>
<p>The number of shares in the offering was lowered for the second time to 2.3 million from 2.4 million. Initially, the company proposed to offer 3.0 million shares.</p>
</text>
